  },
  {
    q: 'What should an AEO ROI model include?',
    a: 'A defensible AEO ROI model should include: a baseline citation audit, a defined query set representing commercial intent, monthly tracking of leading indicators across at least three AI platforms, a methodology for connecting branded search and direct traffic changes to AEO milestones, and conservative revenue assumptions based on your own historical close rates applied to AI-influenced pipeline estimates.'
  }
